org.jamwiki.model

Class GroupMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jamwiki.model.GroupMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class GroupMap
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class is a container for managing groups and their members. It can be instantiated in two different modes:
    • As a group containing members.
    • As a member with a list of the groups he belongs to.
    * @author cclavadetscher
    See Also:
